@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lpdkxx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.01 + tmp + 1.00)) - wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.03)))
    tmp = (wp.sin(v0) - (0.48 + (tmp + 0.42 - v1 + 1.00)))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.sin(v0))
    data[tid] = v0
